        requirements = {
            {name = 'Rusty Medal', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = '1. While the quest Ode to the Serpents is active, speak to Talhaal in Al Zahbi (H-6).\n2. Speak to Fari-Wari in Aht Urhgan Whitegate (K-12).\n3. In Wajaom Woodlands kill Wajaom Tigers until you get a Rusty Medal.\n   - Tigers spawn near (E-8), (F-7) and (K-9).\n4. Go to the Leypoint in Wajaom Woodlands (G-8) and trade the Rusty Medal for a cutscene that completes the quest.\n   - Return to the teahouse and speak to Fari-Wari again to learn Trust:Zazarg\nYou may only get the cutscenes in when General Zazarg is in Al Zahbi.',
