        },
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Mhasbaf in Aht Urhgan Whitegate at (J-8) to begin this quest.\n2. Walk downstairs to the pillar at (J-8) for a cutscene.\n3. Speak to Tohka Telposkha at (I-8) for a cutscene.\n   - You must tell the Galka to go to Port Ephramad.\n     - If you choose any other option, you must select again until you pick Port Ephramad. (You may find selecting the incorrect port entertaining.)\n4. Talk to Rubahah at (F-9) and repeat this process, and then Cacaroon at (G-11) and do the same thing.\n5. Walk to (I-11) (Down the ramp beside the ferry) for a cutscene to obtain the [Key Item] Letter from Bernahn.\n6. Speak to Tataroon at (G-8) in Nashmau to complete the quest and obtain your reward.',
