        walkthrough = '1. Speak with Mishhar near HP#1 in Whitegate.\n   - Requires a JP Midnight wait after Give Peace a Chance\n2. Go to the Teahouse (J-12) for another cutscene.\n3. Return to Mishhar (H-8)\n4. Enter Mamook from (D-12) in Wajaom Woodlands and click on a nearby ???\n   - The ??? is right next to the Survival Guide\n   - Using the Mamook Survival Guide will put you at the correct entrance\n5. Head to Jade Sepulcher and click the BCNM entrance ("Ornamental Door") for a cutscene\n   - Use Aht Urghan Whitegate -> Bhaflau Thickets HP #1 will make this fast\n6. Click again to enter the BCNM: "Moment of Truth"\n7. Blacktattoo Vedool Ja (BLM)\n8. Shadowhand Kajeel Ja (NIN)\n9. Whitetattoo Rahool Ja (WHM)\n   - They do not aggro if you one-shot them from a distance.\n   - You are assisted by three NPCs, one paired with each Mamool.\n     - These must not die.\n10. Return to Mishhar for your reward\n   - You get medicine that depends on your job.\n     - Vile Elixir +1 - RDM, BLU\n     - Pro-Ether +1 - SMN\n     - Intelligence Potion - BLM, SCH\n     - Vitality Potion - PLD, RUN\n     - Agility Potion - RNG, COR, NIN\n     - Dexterity Potion - PUP\n     - Mind Potion - WHM\n     - Strength Potion - WAR, MNK, DRK, DRG\n     - Charisma Potion - BST, BRD, DNC\n     - Hermes Quencher - THF\n     - Icarus Wing - SAM',
