ended period of time.\n10. After winning the battle, you will enter a cutscene where you will choose your reward.\n11. Examine Imperial Whitegate at Aht Urhgan Whitegate (L-8/9) for a cutscene.\n12. Speak to Naja Salaheem in Aht Urhgan Whitegate (I-10) for a cutscene to complete the quest.  (And to feel very dirty on the inside.)',
